S

SerialReader - Class in com.telemetryui.telemetryui
This class is responsible to read specific formated data from the Serial bus and write them as DataSet3D's to Source Objects for further Data transfer.
setSourceManager(SourceManager) - Method in class com.telemetryui.telemetryui.DataChannelController
This method is required to call, so that the instance gets a reference of the @see SourceManager
setSourceManager(SourceManager) - Method in class com.telemetryui.telemetryui.MainController
This method needs to be called to give this Object a reference to the SourceManager so the DataChannel can access the Sources and corresponding data.
Source - Class in com.telemetryui.telemetryui
This class holds a LinkedQueue of Datasets and gets used to transfere DataSets between sources(@see SerialReader or @see DataGenerator) and Sinks(@see DataChannel).
SourceManager - Class in com.telemetryui.telemetryui
This class manages different Source objects so Sinks can access them.

start(Stage) - Method in class com.telemetryui.telemetryui.MainApplication

Mainly used for stopping running Threads.
